Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:34.03,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆鲁大人，该去视察建设工地了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.53,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,我带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.29,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.79,Default,Na,0,0,0,,利姆鲁很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:47.29,Default,Na,0,0,0,,今天紫苑和朱菜也在争夺自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.84,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,因为史莱姆的身体抱起来很舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:58.34,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我有时候也会抱着自己的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.86,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,分身 分身之后分给她们不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:03.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:04.93,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,真要那么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:08.92,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,{\clip(755.185,892.373,755.185,892.373)}也给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.06,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,请也给我一份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.36,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,利姆鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.52,Default,Ranga,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.61,Default,Rigurd,0,0,0,,请务必给我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.19,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,会开始一场有别于命名的死亡战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:22.12,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然需要这个史莱烟身体的代替品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.91,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HA6BDCA&\bord12\shad0\fs60\an5\pos(375.999,708)\frx6\fry18\frz3.726}S\Nl\Ni\Nm\Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.91,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,木雕史莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.58,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,雕塑史莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.66,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,金属制作的金属史莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不 应该不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果没有我这样的柔软度就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.92,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,类似于我身体的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:36.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.55,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,啊...要堕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,能让生物堕落的靠枕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.43,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那玩意就触觉来说应该差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,做个和我一样的懒人靠枕 其名为 利姆鲁靠枕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这不是挺可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:54.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,很像抽奖的头奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.86,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,最大的那个就当作特等奖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.20,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,嗯哼 能先放开我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.12,Default,Both,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我有件事想要拜托朱菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.96,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,好的 请吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.41,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我有样东西想做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:21.22,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果我说是弹性素材她大概也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:26.47,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那个 你能做出滑溜溜还有弹性的布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.93,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,滑溜溜还有弹性...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.74,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.42,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,是像氨纶一样的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,居然能明自？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.07,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,凭感觉猜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,女人的直觉 朱菜你真是个可怕的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.82,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,那个的话很简单 包在我的身上吧 利姆鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.46,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,接下来就是填充物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.08,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,泡沫塑料？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.58,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,那种材料是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:57.42,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那个 粒状的塑料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.26,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,塑料是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,用发泡聚苯乙烯做的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.57,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,发泡聚苯乙烯？？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.14,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,发泡聚苯乙烯就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.95,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs90\c&HCDE3E5&}告知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.34,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,说明 充气成型的聚苯乙烯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.44,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(837,1)}聚苯乙烯是合成树脂的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.02,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,苯乙烯的聚合物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.65,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,嗯 看来说不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:22.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,有没有像是沙子一样 表面光滑的颗粒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:27.24,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,好像和白沙挺接近的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.28,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,白沙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.46,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,森林的深处有一处大湖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.32,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,我听说湖心岛的沙子就是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.83,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,被大自然研磨而成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.59,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,那沙子应该就如同利姆露大人您一样光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.09,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,听起来不错啊 赶紧去取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.49,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,去取白沙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.76,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,虽然不知道您用来干嘛 但最好还是不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.59,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:53.10,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,因为湖里栖息着魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.89,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,哇呜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.36,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,如果被抓住了脚的话 最后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:06.28,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,会被一点一点的拖入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:09.18,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,流传着这样的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.40,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,嘛对于利姆露大人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.51,Default,Garm,0,0,0,,就算遇到了魔物也不会出事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.40,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,是我杞人忧天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.45,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那是什么好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:28.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这附近应该不会有来袭击我们的魔物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,况且我一个人去也会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.72,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我们一起去取白沙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.08,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,顺便大家一起去野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.73,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,野餐 挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.09,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,水边的探索就包在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:44.65,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.90,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,不愧是加维鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.03,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:56.85,Default,Lizards,0,0,0,,加维鲁 加维鲁...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.28,Default,Soka,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.81,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,能和利姆露大人同去远定我真的很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.79,Default,Ranga,0,0,0,,如果是主人 我愿意追随到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.09,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我都说了只是去湖边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.88,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,您要用白沙来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你们就期待我完工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:11.39,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,要把礼物内容透露给收礼的人还真有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.97,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.96,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,把事情和这些对没兴趣的男人们说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:21.48,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,话说 利古鲁德好像很想要的样子还是对他保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.24,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,请务必让我们协助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,红丸你还挺有干劲的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.37,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:37.87,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,以利姆露大人为原型做的靠枕 得到它的紫苑一定会很珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.58,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,随身携带并且还会注意不要弄脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.71,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,也就是说 紫苑再也不会接近厨房了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.47,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.38,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,这任务可事关重大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.23,Default,Souei,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.70,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,说突话我根本没那么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:59.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,毕竟他们很久之前就知道紫苑的料理有多么的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.23,Default,Hakurou,0,0,0,,老身也去 利姆露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.83,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,师 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.49,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,连白老也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:17.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,就这样在各种意义上值得期待的野餐开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.95,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,总感觉有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.75,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,住在湖里的魔物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:31.01,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果只是传言还好 要是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.52,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.06,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这里像就是伽卢姆所说的湖了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.82,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,也就是说白沙所在的地方就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.13,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.32,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我还想着湖有多恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不是也挺漂亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:00.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 在去取白沙之前先填饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.08,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,, 吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.19,Default,All,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.31,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,这还真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.68,Default,Soka,0,0,0,,兄长大人 那份玉子烧是要给苍影大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:30.23,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.62,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.74,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,请吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:44.96,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,没能阻止她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.29,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,您不是说便当自备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.13,Default,Hakurou,0,0,0,,与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.51,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,我原本做了便当 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.34,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.10,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,因为这个盛器的强度不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.98,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,所以漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:09.23,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,看来装不下我对利姆鲁大人的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:12.76,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,嘛...嘛 装不下的话那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.73,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.83,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,作为替代我做了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.54,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,饭团哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:30.04,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这是什么新型魔物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.77,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,来请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:34.38,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,我向哥布一请教过料理的秘诀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.13,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,秘...秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.80,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,没错 被告知了最重要的是倾注爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.31,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,这是我倾注了很多爱情所做的饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,1)}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.11,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.27,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,那么利姆露大人请
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.12,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,快拦下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.47,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,紫苑下做的饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.01,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,吾辈来拦住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:10.04,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H34495D&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.71,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.70,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H34495D&}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.31,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,超帅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.26,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.52,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,加维鲁大人 满分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:35.17,Default,Lizards,0,0,0,,加维鲁 加维鲁 加维鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:49.27,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,加维鲁大人 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.12,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.17,Default,Lizard,0,0,0,,一脸安详 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.51,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉 给利姆大人的食物居然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:00.23,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,没事 没事 你看我就算不吃也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.18,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,比起这个 快去做下水的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,去取白沙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.19,Default,Na,0,0,0,,所谓的准备就是去换泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:16.77,Default,Na,0,0,0,,矮人们用氨纶做了泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.95,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆鲁大人 感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:34.96,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,稍微有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:51.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,泳装是我设计 伽卢姆他们一同完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.23,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,干得好啊 伽卢姆三兄弟 赞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.69,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,各位都很合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:58.94,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.45,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,为什么连你们也穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不妙 岚牙好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:17.13,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,伽卢姆说也为利姆鲁准备了泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.59,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.30,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.59,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,死库水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.09,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不行不行，这绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.35,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,伽卢姆你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.21,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,嘛 这样倒也还行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.70,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,那 差不多该动身了 利姆鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.60,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,说的也是呢 那大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.36,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:49.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,诶 米莉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.70,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,好过分 为什么野餐不叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.96,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,明明是密友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.17,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:13:00.92,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,怕会发生什么麻烦的事情 这样的话根本说不出囗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊抱歉 我以为你很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.18,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,即使再忙 密友的邀请我也会随时赶来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.43,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,那么 你们现在要去干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,游去湖心岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.72,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,要游泳吗 那我也要游
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.93,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你没带泳装来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.16,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,根本不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.68,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.67,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,真是麻烦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.49,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.76,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,{\clip(1551.386,900.534,1551.386,900.534)}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.87,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,泳装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.38,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,说明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.63,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,{\clip(1833.456,1070.386,1833.456,1070.386)}虽然设计相同但材质不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:46.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好像可以但又感觉不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:51.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好的 大家 伽卢姆所说湖心岛就有白沙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,传闻其中也有魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:55.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,各位行动要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.89,Default,All,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.94,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,魔物什么的随出来也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.81,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,喂无论出现什么 你也绝对不能动手哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:07.80,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你会把这附近都毁掉的 约好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.78,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.42,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,好凉快呀 好舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.32,Default,Gobta,0,0,0,,真的很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:19.42,Default,Gabiru,0,0,0,,让我想起故乡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:30.27,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,并没有感受到什么强大的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.20,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,关于魔物的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:37.10,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,可能只是溺水的事件被添油加醋传出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,如果是那样就好了 不过注意点没啥坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.02,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.51,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我的脚好像被海藻之类的东西缠住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:23.44,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,不 不要 这是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.12,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利 利姆鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.94,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,朱菜 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.22,Default,Soka,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.04,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,看起来好色情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,色情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.72,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.88,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,水刃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.72,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,利姆鲁是大人的斩击居然无效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.03,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.85,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,魔物的本体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:25.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,喂 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:34.24,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,上面的同伴很困扰 能停下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.97,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,它的攻击很鲁莽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.43,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这不像是攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.75,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,更像是在痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.94,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这家伙到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:51.48,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H291517&\pos(660,60)}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.28,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,居然吃了这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以才暴走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:08.29,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,毕竟这个等级的魔物也不常见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:12.05,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,等一下我现在就让你解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.83,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,动作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.02,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:25.52,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,难道是利姆鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.53,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.37,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你在找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.36,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,你难不成看不见周围吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.46,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那么照我说的做做看？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.13,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,有个叫「魔力感知」的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.34,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,在这种地方孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,, 而且还什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:04.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我能明白你哟 因为我最初也是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.54,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我和那家伙都很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.75,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以无论是史莱姆 还是 巨大的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,也成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.52,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,在那之后我不在孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,接受了许多委托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:22.20,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,但结果都是因为我害怕寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.62,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,哦 看来你看得见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:32.04,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,乖 那我差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.88,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,露骨地显示出寂寞了 和某条龙—样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:41.30,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那个 我想要湖心岛的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以今后会时不时来取
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:48.74,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,很快就会再来见你的 所以别那么寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.70,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,抱歉 让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.07,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,我和魔物谈妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.57,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,利姆鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.96,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.48,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,利姆鲁大人 请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,等一下 这里面有很深的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:35.73,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.24,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,因为某种原因他得到了很强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.11,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,所以暂时暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.67,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,给我个面子放过他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.04,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,那没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.87,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,但是 为什么会暴走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:53.19,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,谁知道 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:57.63,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H34001E&\pos(1650,120)}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.55,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H8F5861&\pos(960,60)}咕咕咕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:06.15,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那个...那个 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.56,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,咦我们脚下的沙子超级滑溜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.03,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,照你这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.56,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,是呢 难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.90,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,滑溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.40,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这就是白沙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:22.61,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,滑溜溜 滑溜溜的白沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.62,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,这个沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.51,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,包含了大量水分的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.12,Default,Great Sage,0,0,0,,被魔物的粘液所研磨而成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.79,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:41.61,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,因为这家伙栖息在这附件 所以形成了这些沙子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.55,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,好 这里的沙子我们都拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:48.79,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,诶？我们带的袋子不够装
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:52.43,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不用一次全部拿走 我们时不时来现就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.43,Default,Milim,0,0,0,,{\an8}滑溜溜 滑溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:56.89,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,虽然能够全部装到胃袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.19,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不过和这家伙还有约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.73,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,还会再来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:12.07,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,今天我做了能够恢复精神的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.58,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,不 偶尔也尝下我亲手做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:19.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,那个 靠枕已经不要了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:23.01,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,要的 我会带回去好好使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.38,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,不，那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:30.13,Default,Beni,0,0,0,,还是比不过真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.21,Default,Shion,0,0,0,,照顾利姆露大人也是我重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:38.10,Default,Shuna,0,0,0,,太狡猾了请让我也一起照顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:42.11,Default,Rimuru,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 随她们便吧
